messages.text: did you tell them
hello to you too
did you
shouldn’t you be studying
there’s no point
I’m certainly not going to tell them if you fail math
if you would tutor me, I wouldn’t fail
“tutor”
“tutor” ;)
go study
what if I come over to your place?
just to study
honestly
maybe I’ll feel more motivated around you
you mean so you can introduce yourself to my parents
well you aren’t doing it
please stop
I told my parents
your parents are american
you’re american
but my parents are indian
can you drop this? and go study.
and let me study.
your mom likes me, you know. I stay and chat with her after class sometimes
WHAT?! Shut up. You do not do that
I do. mrs gupta loves me
wait, do I have to call her auntie?
that’s racist
HOW IS THAT RACIST? don’t you call everyone auntie?
you’re such an american
she told me she studied in london
yeah she did
you never told me that
why would I have told you where my parents studied? I don’t know where your parents studied
you always go on about how conservative and Indian they are. studying in London doesn’t sound like that
whatever. it was a long time ago
did your parents have an arranged marriage?
yes. J, please stop wasting my time right now. our grades from this semester still go on our applications
that’s basically like online dating, right?
what are you talking about?
arranged marriage. we read about it for our global studies class
arranged marriages were basically set up based on like two people’s resumes, right? and maybe pictures?
I guess. but your parents pick for you
I’m going to go to the chem lab tomorrow and give your mother my resume and picture and ask her to arrange our marriage
hello? are you still there?
yes. I’m trying to study though. stop texting.
your mother just emailed me.
she did not
she did!
about what?
she wants to know where I’m going to college next year
what? are you serious? why?
because she loves me
kidding. relax SERIOUS SONIA. she emailed the whole class
I’ll answer
NO don’t answer. this is weird.
I have to! she’s a teacher
WHAT ARE YOU WRITING
I’m telling her I’m going to go to college wherever her daughter goes to college
STOP
oh my god. do not write that. I’m serious
DO NOT EMAIL MY MOTHER
too late
what did you write?
don’t worry about it
dude, she replied already. auntie emails fast
I’m going to call her and ask her what she’s doing
damn it. she isn’t picking up. what is she emailing you now?
Jason. answer. this isn’t funny.
I have a question. so if your parents were looking for a husband for you and they got my resume and picture, do you think they would select me?
WAIT. okay, I’m me but I’m indian. like everything else is the same about me. I still play squash, I still want to go to Ohio State, I still hang out with Auntie in the chem lab. Only I’m indian.
I don’t know
I bet they would
not if you fail math
are you still emailing her?
I’ve never eaten home cooked indian food
I don’t know how to cook. sorry.
I know. I wouldn’t pick you for my arranged marriage. I love Indian food
my mother makes samosas from scratch. I’ll bring you some if you let me study now
samosas, you say. I’ll email her and tell her I heard she makes good samosas
Jason, please stop emailing her. she’s going to get really weirded out
you know I’m not joking about wanting to go to college where you go
I know. and that’s sweet. but I don’t want to talk about this stuff over text
you never want to talk about it in person either
you don’t know what it’s like being Indian, okay
I see your mother in class every single day. you make her sound a lot scarier than she is. Steph spilled diet coke all over the beakers and your mother laughed
she needs to stop drinking diet coke all the time. her teeth look gray
anyway it’s different with me. I’m her daughter. you won’t understand
hey. are you still there?
Jason
Jason, come on. don’t get grumpy
it’s really hard, okay. my family isn’t like yours. I don’t talk to my parents about this stuff. all their friends are Indian.
your mother has lunch with mrs. Norris every single day. She’s not Indian
that’s different
she just emailed me again
seriously stop emailing her
come on
it was almost funny in the beginning but it’s totally not anymore
she wants to know if I’ve met her daughter
shit. I bet she knows something.
shit shit shit
Just tell her we’re in the same math class and then stop emailing with her, please
please
have you stopped?
J?
see you tonight at 7
we don’t have plans tonight
I know. But auntie just invited me over for dinner to eat samosas and meet her daughter
